              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "A 6Li beam energy of 32 MeV to assure a predominantly",
                " direct reaction mechanism. 7Li beam energy of 16 MeV.",
                " The typical Li beam intensity varied between 100 and",
                " 500 nA on target."
              ]
            }
          ],
