              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SCIN"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " A 100 cm broad-range magnetic spectrograph and",
                " detected at the focal plane with a position-sensitive",
                " proportional counter system backed by a scintillator",
                " to measure position, energy loss and total energy of",
                " the incoming reaction products."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The 180 targets were prepared by evaporating an",
                " approximately 50 microg/cm2 thick layer of W18aO onto",
                " a 380 microg/cm2 gold foil. The thickness of the W18O",
                " layer was determined and possible target contaminants",
                " were identified from the elastic scattering of 6Li at",
                " an energy of 32 MeV."
              ]
            }
